If you want to get a scale, one way is to pull for a burn crew, get a spotter, and make sure the warrior has a sow potion. Then he can pull, and get the scale. The other way is to have a force preassembled at the zone. Today there was a force from Voice of Rallos in EJ waiting for Sev, and another force from Dark Brigade in Skyfire. Both of these mobs were left to the raid forces. (I know VoR killed Sev, not sure if Talendor popped for Dark Brigade).<br>
